Computational Biology and Chemistry
Volume 95 , December 2021, 107587
Computational Biology and Chemistry
Computational algorithmic and molecular dynamics study of functional and structural impacts of non-synonymous single nucleotide polymorphisms in human DHFR gene
Author links open overlay panel Md. Shahed Alam a 1 Md. Abu Saleh a 1 Md. Mozibullah b Ashik Tanvir Riham a Md. Solayman c Siew Hua Gan d
Show more
